CustomField.description: Specify the record level country code to override global country code setting. Value from this field will be added to your Click-to-Call links(only this record). Leave this field blank if your phone numbers already have country code. Example Value: +1
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Specify the record level country code to override global country code setting. Value from this field will be added to your Click-to-Call links(only this record). Leave this field blank if your phone numbers already have country code. Example Value: +1
CustomField.label: Country Code
